WEBVTT
NOTE OE3D — Script3 — Kréyol Gwiyanè

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:01.484
Bonjou !

2
00:00:01.434 --> 00:00:05.900
Lapeau ki an kontak avèk prothèz ou orthèz-ou a mérit yonn atansyon spécyal.

3
00:00:05.900 --> 00:00:09.227
Yonn bon iyijèn koutanné prévien plifò komplikasyon yo.

4
00:00:09.227 --> 00:00:11.483
Vwéla bon jès pou adopté.

5
00:00:12.883 --> 00:00:14.634
Iyijèn chak jou.

6
00:00:14.584 --> 00:00:19.838
Chak swa, lavé lapeau an kontak avèk aparèy-ou a épi dlo tyèd é savon dou pH nétral.

7
00:00:19.838 --> 00:00:23.885
Rinssé bien é séché dousman pa tamponnman, san fwoté.

8
00:00:23.885 --> 00:00:25.802
Jès sa a sé esansyèl.

9
00:00:27.202 --> 00:00:28.720
Prévansyon.

10
00:00:28.670 --> 00:00:33.066
Idraté lapeau apré nétoyaj la, men janmen avan mété aparèy la.

11
00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:37.974
Evité plis lapeau adan aparèy la, é pòté souwètkiltòt adapté san koutir épè.

12
00:00:39.374 --> 00:00:41.065
Siyal alarèm yo.

13
00:00:41.015 --> 00:00:49.179
Kontaktez-nou san tann si ou wè yon wougè ki rete plis ven minit, yon blési, yonn eskèr, yon sant inhabityèl ou yon anflamasyon pa nòmal.

14
00:00:49.179 --> 00:00:51.191
Janmen ignoré siyal sa yo.

15
00:00:52.591 --> 00:00:54.988
Konfò-ou sé pryorité-nou.

16
00:00:54.938 --> 00:00:57.841
Léquip-nou la pou akonpagnié-ou a chak étap.

17
00:00:57.841 --> 00:00:59.949
Pa ezité kontakté-nou.
